txt.en:
Thisarti, a Haradrim master-archer, has snuck up from behind and fires on us with deadly aim. Deal with him quickly so he cannot fire on Aragorn and his troops.

This quest starts with <rgb=#FFFF00>empty</rgb> Merit Rating.

<rgb=#00FF00>Merit Gain:</rgb>
* Defeat Thisarti
* Defeat Thisarti quickly
<rgb=#FF0000>You have left Thisarti unchallenged for too long.</rgb>
<rgb=#FF0000>Defeat Thisarti before he falls back into the Corsair ranks</rgb>
Defeat the archer Thisarti swiftly, for his arrows and his aim are deadly.
<rgb=#FF0000>Defeat Thisarti before he falls back into the Corsair ranks</rgb>
